  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Edition</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/86ee0e90dfc63df9746bdfb6d45d1731.avif?t=1765500475\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras_big/86ee0e90dfc63df9746bdfb6d45d1731.avif?t=1765500475 width=800 height=281 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎉 <strong>Join Our Official Discord for Exclusive Perks!</strong> 🎉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Special Rewards</strong> – Only for our Discord members! <br>🤝 <strong>Direct Access to Developers</strong> – Get quick feedback and updates! <br>🌍 <strong>Connect with Global Players</strong> – Find your perfect party worldwide! <br>🎮 <strong>Explore the Backrooms Together</strong> – Team up with new friends for thrilling adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/bfc7ad4f0fbc6477b8b7c52ea37858c1.avif?t=1765500475\" width=276 height=217 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t miss out on these community-only perks! Join the fun and become part of the Backroom Company family today! 👾💬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“This place cannot be explained with logic. Record. Survive.”</h2>Become a test subject for Async Corp. (hereafter Backroom Company) and explore the unknown space hidden behind the Noclip phenomenon: the “Backrooms.”<br>Your mission is simple. Capture anomalous phenomena and transmit the data while staying alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Official Release on July 30, 2025: Go Deeper</strong><br>Your exploration now goes beyond the hotel, swimming pool, and parking lot—into the foul-smelling “Sewers” and the eerie “School.”<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Exploration Mode</u>: Face the fear of getting lost in ever-changing environments.<br></li><li><u>Story Mode</u>: Follow a fixed map and uncover the massive conspiracy Backroom Company has been hiding.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Core Gameplay: Filming Is Survival</strong><br>Collect strange items scattered throughout the rooms and record unidentified entities to leave evidence.<br>The data you capture becomes your survival score—and your key to escape.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/480ee34c92a66ceb6eda27348fee84cd.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/480ee34c92a66ceb6eda27348fee84cd.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/480ee34c92a66ceb6eda27348fee84cd.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/3a0f7b5cc5e866b624f3cff08b039af1.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/3a0f7b5cc5e866b624f3cff08b039af1.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/3a0f7b5cc5e866b624f3cff08b039af1.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>“Hide or Stay Silent”</strong><br>The beings of the Backrooms do not welcome you.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An immortal entity relentlessly chases you. The locker room is your only safe haven.<br></li><li>A monster without eyes detects even the faintest breath. Muffle your footsteps and hold your breath.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/e497d8612513793ed35c573940bd89a3.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/e497d8612513793ed35c573940bd89a3.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/e497d8612513793ed35c573940bd89a3.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>“Work with Your Team”</strong><br>Team up with your companions. But remember: more terrifying than any entity may be a teammate in panic.<br><i>(No matter how angry you get, try not to kill your teammates on purpose. Probably.)</i><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“This place cannot be explained with logic. Record. Survive.”</h2>Become a test subject for Async Corp. (hereafter Backroom Company) and explore the unknown space hidden behind the Noclip phenomenon: the “Backrooms.”<br>Your mission is simple. Capture anomalous phenomena and transmit the data while staying alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Official Release on July 30, 2025: Go Deeper</strong><br>Your exploration now goes beyond the hotel, swimming pool, and parking lot—into the foul-smelling “Sewers” and the eerie “School.”<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Exploration Mode</u>: Face the fear of getting lost in ever-changing environments.<br></li><li><u>Story Mode</u>: Follow a fixed map and uncover the massive conspiracy Backroom Company has been hiding.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f6